data.description: Super cute single story with finished walk-out basement is on just over a half acre lot. ramp leads to front door for wheelchair access. 2 nice size rooms and full bath on main level with tall ceilings and lots of old world charm! Brand new roof, new front and back deck. wheel chair access from covered front porch. all new paint to include kitchen cabinets, new counter tops, and new ceiling fans in living area and both bedrooms. Walkout basement with plenty of room and where the 3rd room is located. completely fenced with shed, raised garden beds and chicken coup!
